{"tid":800494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美部長：中國恐少報非洲豬瘟疫情","createTime":"2018-08-31T02:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T06:43:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b69e9c6217b49e24dce838a10b91a7659d5295b8","tid":800494,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:20:22.000Z","msg":"美國農業部長帕度(Sonny Perdue)30日表示，中國豬隻爆發的非洲豬瘟(ASF)疫情，情況可能比公開報導還要嚴重，並擔心一旦疫情進入美國「破壞性極大」。<br />\n<br />\n帕度說，中國恐怕有低報非洲豬瘟疫情，他們認為在中國可能有少報，中方可以控制媒體這麼做。<br />\n<br />\n中國本月3日通報在遼寧省發現致命非洲豬瘟首例。中國農業農村部3日在官網發布「答記者問」表示，遼寧省瀋陽市瀋北新區發生非洲豬瘟疫情，農業農村部已同時向國際組織通報疫情。<br />\n<br />\n而在2週後，河南省鄭州出現另一波非洲豬瘟疫情。<br />\n<br />\n相關疫情已推升美國豬價，並升高外界對這種疾病擴散到亞洲其他地區的憂心。帕度表示，一旦非洲豬瘟疫情進入美國，不但豬隻會受到感染，連糧食處理人員和種植動物飼料的農民都會受到影響，將造成「極大破壞」。<br />\n<br />\n中國農業農村部29日表示，今年8月以來，遼寧、河南、江蘇、浙江4省，先後發生非洲豬瘟疫情，病毒汙染狀況有待進一步調查，「不排除繼續出現新發疫情的可能」。而中國當局30日則表示，安徽省蕪湖農場有185隻豬受到感染，是8月以來第五波非洲豬瘟疫情。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯、東歐和非洲已發現非洲豬瘟病例，東亞之前未曾發現過，這是對豬隻最具毀滅性疾病之一。不過中國官方強調，已禁止疫區產品流出，而且非洲豬瘟不感染人，對人體健康和食品安全沒有直接影響，可以放心吃豬肉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E6%9B%B4%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D-%E7%BE%8E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%81%90%E5%B0%91%E5%A0%B1%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%B1%AC%E7%98%9F%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-004200541.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D-%25E7%25BE%258E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E7%2598%259F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-004200541.html&d=YaD4eHlGJtkOGsmHzZwWNcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=00ca5dc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E6%9B%B4%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D-%E7%BE%8E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%81%90%E5%B0%91%E5%A0%B1%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%B1%AC%E7%98%9F%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-004200541.html</a>"},{"pid":"e34ea173481f3dd8e8e99bb694093a25e100d550","tid":800494,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:21:35.000Z","msg":"又係美國佬搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc9d193db28c6416a13117ad9cf9695e70889f8","tid":800494,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:22:28.000Z","msg":"可放心食用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ca9cd6dd0cd3cdc552273066d10ae81af2953d","tid":800494,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有毒氣體不會對人體有害</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1beaec71ceebad22d559dc7bc2dafd092c5c22ed","tid":800494,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/wVXQQcU7N8A/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FwVXQQcU7N8A%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=95350a8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b66f49316fe5dd2a55e2610e57dc7e1b963e3a5b","tid":800494,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"對人體健康和食品安全沒有直接影響，可以放心吃豬肉。<br />\n<br />\n佢叫人少食<br />\n可能啲人重會食<br />\n咁講點信你啊戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92f57d53edf4d4432f5a8f2efdaca73b62691a7","tid":800494,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:30:06.000Z","msg":"懷疑豬隻收受美國資助發瘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03e3c8cb6da8d26d74542b20f9b0ecfe989c5b3","tid":800494,"uid":3508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T02:31:23.000Z","msg":"又搞事<br />\n沒事兒沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomo